HEADWORD: Smithsonian
<hw>Smith*so"ni*an</hw> <pr>(-s⟦omac⟧"n⟦icr⟧*⟦ait⟧n)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<def>Of or pertaining to the Englishman J. L. M.
<etsep>Smithson</etsep>, or to the national institution of learning
which he endowed at Washington, D. C.; <as>as, the <ex>Smithsonian</ex>
Institution; <ex>Smithsonian</ex> Reports</as>.</def> --
<def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>The Smithsonian Institution.</def></def2><--
capitalized -->⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

